<div dir="ltr">Hmm,<div><br></div><div>On a different Linux/x86-64 host things work as expected with &#39;-lutil&#39; linked explicitly:</div><div><br></div><div><div>$ ./INST/bin/mpicc -showme BLD/examples/hello_c.c </div>

